Simple p2p realtime chat which visually resembles UNIX 'talk'

Get / build / run:

$ git clone git://github.com/gammy/cheaptalk.git
$ cd cheaptalk
$ make
$ ./cheaptalk

Change color of the text by hitting ESC followed by r,g,b or a number from 
0 (default) to 6. You should be able to move around your window with the arrow
keys.
